{
  "stem": "13313.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't buy a dozen eggs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was a purchase, a major purchase to buy one egg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So one day, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Roggeman sends me to this particular farm because we did all-- we did all the buying and shopping and everything else, to buy the egg.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I get to this farm, and they knew me already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the farmer's son, all very healthy people and very well, a big boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, well-- he start to play with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I played with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the way you played, a very popular sport in the fall or beginning of the winter was there are these wild chestnuts were growing on these trees and we used to knock them down because you'd play all kind of games with those chestnuts.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a question  of knocking down chestnuts from the tree.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had so little opportunity to really play that it was so nice of the little kid to play with me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the farmer boy played with me to throw down the chestnuts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a very happy half hour.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the half hour, I wanted to take my hanky out  of my pocket and before I realized it that egg in my pocket had been crushed in my pocket from playing with this boy.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I start to get panicky, because I knew what was going to happen to me if I come home without the egg or with a-- and with a dirty pocket and without the 25 francs.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told the boy, I says look, I says, I really can't go home without the egg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is there any way that you could give me another egg?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
